name: Imam Kikou - Papuy PSBB(Extended Remastered)(Audio Visual)
description: Papuy(n): is a dizzy or headache from thoughts and situation. PSBB(Pembatasan Sosial Berskala Besar) means Large Scale Social Distancing in English. In Bahasa, the song title means "headache from social distancing situation". This song was created in May 2020 by Imam Kikou because of his unemployment status cause by Covid-19. In early 2021, he remastered this with proper sound tuning & addition of audio visual from Mamedz. Here's the audio visual NFT ready for sale exclusively in 5 pcs.
